01:18:21,920 --> 01:18:27,440
children of Stickytoes the Tree Toad. Of 
course Farmer Brown's Boy didn't let him.  

811
01:18:28,000 --> 01:18:33,440
He made little Mr. Gartersnake set 
Master Stickytoes free and held Mr.

812
01:18:33,440 --> 01:18:38,000
Gartersnake until Master 
Stickytoes was safely out of reach.

813
01:18:40,000 --> 01:18:40,960
