01:22:10,960 --> 01:22:18,720
Pasture that made his smile still broader. He saw 
Farmer Brown's boy filling a great tin pail with  

847
01:22:18,720 --> 01:22:25,040
blueberries, and he knew that Farmer Brown's boy 
didn't know that Buster Bear was anywhere about,  

848
01:22:25,760 --> 01:22:32,800
and he knew that Buster Bear didn't know that 
Farmer Brown's boy was anywhere about, and somehow  

