01:23:29,440 --> 01:23:34,800
Yes, it was perfectly harmless. Buster 
gave a little sigh of pure happiness.  

859
01:23:35,360 --> 01:23:41,520
He would eat those berries to the last one, 
and then he would go home to the Green Forest.

860
01:23:43,040 --> 01:23:44,000
