907
01:28:46,080 --> 01:28:48,000
SAMMY JAY MAKES THINGS WORSE

908
01:28:48,000 --> 01:28:48,880
FOR BUSTER BEAR

909
01:28:50,160 --> 01:28:57,280
"Thief, thief, thief! Thief, thief, thief!" 
