910
01:28:57,280 --> 01:29:01,120
as he followed Buster Bear across the 
Old Pasture towards the Green Forest.  

911
01:29:01,920 --> 01:29:06,640
Never had he screamed so loud, and 
never had his voice sounded so excited.  

912
01:29:07,520 --> 01:29:12,640
The little people of the Green Forest, the 
Green Meadows, and the Smiling Pool are so  

913
01:29:12,640 --> 01:29:19,760
used to hearing Sammy cry thief that usually they 
think very little about it. But every blessed one  

914
01:29:19,760 --> 01:29:25,520
who heard Sammy this morning stopped whatever 
